1. Asia

#Singapore

Prof. Zhi Ning Chen, IEEE Fellow

National University of Singapore

Research Interests:

Electromagnetic engineering; antennas/sensors for communication, radar, and imaging; sensing systems.

Homepage:

http://ece.nus.edu.sg/drupal/?q=node/135

ResearchGate:

https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Zhi_Ning_Chen/?ev=prf_act



Prof. Zhongxiang Shen, IEEE Fellow

Nanyang Technological University

Research Interests:

Small and planar antennas, thin absorbing layers, hybrid numerical techniques for modeling.

Homepage:

http://www.ntu.edu.sg/home/ezxshen/index.htm



Prof. Yong Xin Guo, IEEE Fellow

National University of Singapore

Research Interests:

Antenna, RF circuits, monolithic microwave integrated circuit (MMIC), biomedical applications. 

Homepage:

https://www.ece.nus.edu.sg/stfpage/eleguoyx/


