http://www.ee.cuhk.edu.hk/~klwu/

 

Prof. Lijun Jiang, IEEE Fellow

University of HongKong

Research Interests:

Large-scale heterogeneous electromagnetics, VLSI power integrity and signal integrity,nano-scale electromagnetism for THz and optoelectronics, and microwave material engineering inspired by nano optics.

Homepage:

https://www.eee.hku.hk/people/ljiang/

